'''格拉斯哥笑容'''（也被称为'''切尔西笑容'''，或'''柴郡猫'''）指的是从受害者的嘴角划到耳根上的[[傷口|伤口]]，留下一道类似微笑的[[疤痕|疤痕]] <ref>{{cite web|author=Mills, Rod|url=http://www.express.co.uk/posts/view/68037/Surgeon-says-hospitals-treat-a-knife-victim-every-six-hours|work=[[每日快報|The Daily Express]]|title=Surgeon Says Hospitals Treat a Knife Victim Every Six Hours|date=October 27, 2008|accessdate=November 20, 2009|archive-date=2009-07-04|archive-url=http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20090704154009/http://www.express.co.uk/posts/view/68037/Surgeon-says-hospitals-treat-a-knife-victim-every-six-hours|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/city-slicker-glasgow-1616900.html|title=City Slicker Glasgow|work=[[獨立報|The Independent]]|accessdate=November 20, 2009|location=London|first=John|last=Arlidge|date=April 24, 1995|archive-date=2009-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091216055130/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/city-slicker-glasgow-1616900.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

这种伤口一般是用[[多用途刀|小刀]]或碎玻璃制造的，留下一道令受害者终身[[微笑|微笑]]的疤痕<ref>{{citation |title=Maxillofacial trauma and esthetic facial reconstruction |page=555 |author1=Peter Ward Booth |author2=Barry L. Eppley |author3=Rainer Schmelzeisen |year=2003 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8tdpAAAAMAAJ |publisher={{tsl|en|Churchill Livingstone||Churchill Livingstone}} |isbn=9780443071249 |accessdate=2020-08-09 |archive-date=2017-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170410133001/https://books.google.com/books?id=8tdpAAAAMAAJ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

这种行为据说始于20世纪20年代与30年代，起源于[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]][[格拉斯哥|格拉斯哥]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/scottish-news/razor-gangs-ruled-the-streets-but-even-960790|title=Razor gangs ruled the streets but even in the violence of pre-war years, one man stood out|date=October 19, 2007|author=McKay, Reg|work=[[每日紀事報|每日紀事報]]|location=[[格拉斯哥|格拉斯哥]]|accessdate=January 12, 2019|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301061128/https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/scottish-news/razor-gangs-ruled-the-streets-but-even-960790|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

值得一提，[[蘇格蘭人|苏格兰]]演员[[汤米·弗拉纳根|汤米·弗拉纳根]]在苏格兰一家酒吧外面遭到袭击，留下了格拉斯哥笑容的疤痕<ref>{{cite web|last1=Fretts|first1=Bruce|date=November 12, 2014|title=Sons of Anarchy's Tommy Flanagan on Those Facial Scars, This Final Season, and Chibs|url=http://www.vulture.com/2014/11/sons-of-anarchy-interview-tommy-flanagan.html|access-date=January 12, 2019|website=[[紐約_(雜誌)|紐約 (雜誌)]]|publisher=[[New_York_(magazine)|New York]]|archive-date=2015-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150213033615/http://www.vulture.com/2014/11/sons-of-anarchy-interview-tommy-flanagan.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

